WEBVTT

00:02.900 --> 00:04.340
Admit it. We're lost.

00:04.350 --> 00:07.460
No,we're not. The Naveer Pass
is just beyond that ridge.

00:07.850 --> 00:10.200
Hey,Wizard,you know what
power I wish you had?

00:10.210 --> 00:11.640
The power to admit
when you're wrong.

00:11.660 --> 00:14.970
Right now I'd settle
for a silencing spell.

00:14.980 --> 00:17.920
At the next tavern, we're
asking for directions.

00:18.320 --> 00:20.560
- Kahlan.
- Wait.

00:25.500 --> 00:27.410
Kahlan Amnell?

00:29.000 --> 00:35.074
Learn the unknown English words
of this movie at www.skeebdo.com

00:38.760 --> 00:40.500
*******

00:47.810 --> 00:49.940
********

00:51.180 --> 00:55.660
My dear Kahlan,I knew
Mira would lead us to you.

00:59.870 --> 01:01.000
Serena?

01:01.020 --> 01:04.459
Zeddicus Zu'l
Zorander. My old friend.

01:04.470 --> 01:07.770
Mother Confessor?
This is Richard Cypher.

01:09.170 --> 01:11.370
The Seeker of Truth.

01:11.380 --> 01:13.510
This is truly an honor.

01:14.200 --> 01:16.200
Erin. Tara.

01:16.210 --> 01:17.960
Alana.

01:21.460 --> 01:23.370
I thought you were all in hiding.

01:23.380 --> 01:25.420
We were.

01:25.430 --> 01:29.200
But Darken Rahl's spies were
more insidious than we thought.

01:29.210 --> 01:32.130
They uncovered our houses of refu.

01:32.490 --> 01:35.620
There's no safety for Confessors
in the Midlands anymore.

01:35.640 --> 01:37.510
That's why we've been
searching for you.

01:37.530 --> 01:39.990
We must leave until the
time of Rahl's defeat.

01:40.000 --> 01:43.060
We have no choice but to
seek sanctuary in Valeria.

01:43.290 --> 01:44.980
Valeria?

01:44.990 --> 01:48.640
It's an island,hidden by
magic. Far off the coast.

01:48.650 --> 01:49.960
So you're fleeing?

01:49.990 --> 01:51.820
Only temporarily.

01:51.830 --> 01:54.780
When Rahl is vanquished
we will return.

01:54.800 --> 01:59.460
But Mother Confessor, we're the
source of justice in the Midlands.

01:59.480 --> 02:01.970
The people need us
now more than ever.

02:01.990 --> 02:04.380
Rahl wants a world without justice.

02:04.400 --> 02:07.040
And by killing us, he'll get it.

02:07.890 --> 02:11.140
We wanted to give you the
opportunity to join us.

02:15.240 --> 02:17.980
You know I can't
abandon my mission.

02:19.930 --> 02:22.100
I expected so.

02:22.110 --> 02:24.310
But the decision need to be yours.

02:24.320 --> 02:26.590
Mother Confessor, we
need to keep moving.

02:26.610 --> 02:29.100
Rahl's quads are tracking us.

02:29.920 --> 02:33.050
We've managed to stay ahead of them,
but we can't let our guard down.

02:33.060 --> 02:34.690
We'll escort you to the coast.

02:34.710 --> 02:37.240
Will the other
Confessors meet us there?

02:40.030 --> 02:42.740
There are no other
Confessors,Kahlan.

02:43.190 --> 02:45.870
We are all that's left.

